# Public alt-data summary: small (~3KB), sanitised, committable digest of the
# private runtime cache at cache/alt_data/providers/*.json. Generated by
# scripts/export_public_summary.py and refreshed every 30 minutes by the
# Celery beat task ``alt_data.export_public_summary``. See docs/alt_data_audit.md § 14.
!data/public/
!data/public/**

# Output / Reports / Metrics (runtime generated)
output/
tmp/
reports/
metrics/
profiles/
backups/

# ML model artifacts (keep directories, ignore generated weights/scalers)
